        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> The current implementation requires you to show empty spaces with the same width click label, instead of showing nothing. I haven't run into problems with that approach.\n\nProblems I am experiencing with this approach is that it requires to know the width of the empty space in advance. Which can be a problem when all that is needed is using `%l` or `%s`. This requires doing not only non-trivial computations but also caching to be performant.",
            "created_at": "2026-06-13T14:32:05Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/40210#issuecomment-4698808381",
